#######ELB###########
Its automatically routes incoming traffic across dynamically changing number of multiple instances
Its acts as a single point of contact for all incoming traffic to the instances in auto scaling group
It is used to monitor the health of the registered instances so the load balancer send the requested traffic to heathy instances
Blue green deployments in aws

#######Auto scaling########
Its scales infrastructure when ever we needed
Automatically increase and decrease the scaling group
Adds new instances when load reaches certain level and spin down when no longer needed
Auto scaling is automatically registered with the load balancer this is increase the fault tolarance of application
Fault tolarance = Enaables a system to continue operating properly in the event of failure

